import React from 'react'
import{Box, Typography,TextField,Button}from '@mui/material'
const Register = () => {
  return (
      <>
          <Box maxWidth={450} display="flex" flexDirection={"column"} alignItems="center" justifyContent={"center"} margin="auto" marginTop={5} boxShadow="10px 10px 2px #ccc">
              <Typography>Register</Typography>
              <TextField />
              <TextField />
              <TextField />
              <TextField />
              <Button>Submit</Button>
              <Button>Already Registerd ? Please Login</Button>
          </Box>
    </>
  )
}

export default Register
